{"id": "11387", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11387", "title": "Healing Ritual (Original Sin 2)", "text": "Healing Ritual is an &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;adept Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\n is a supportive hydrosophist skill that allows caster to send forth an unpredictable wave of healing energy that restores Vitality of all affected allies and deals physical damage to all &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; characters or characters affected by &lt;a href=\"Decaying%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Decaying&lt;/a&gt; status effect. The wave may affect the caster as well if they are close enough but they cannot target themselves with it. \nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophy\"&gt;Hydrosophy&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects. skill physical damage is reflected back when the undead target is under &lt;a href=\"Deflective%20Barrier\"&gt;Deflective Barrier&lt;/a&gt; skill, however it will do no damage (Definitive Edition only).\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 2 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Hydrosophist\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 500 gold. A skillbook can be crafted if a scroll is combined with a &lt;a href=\"Blank%20Water%20Skillbook\"&gt;Blank Water Skillbook&lt;/a&gt;. Since is an adept Hydrosophist skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; reach level 9.\n scroll is a magical item that allows any character to cast skill, regardless of skill prerequisites, but only once. The only limiting element in casting this way is the amount of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Action%20Points\"&gt;Action Points (AP)&lt;/a&gt; character has at their disposal in current turn. The scroll is craftable, weights 0.02 and has base value of 260 gold.\nThe cost of Action Points between scroll and skill themselves remains the same. Both the scroll and the skill itself are affected by other skills, items, abilities and talents that may provide additional bonuses.\nSkill Modifiers.\n is a supportive skill whose effects depend on the following characteristics of the caster:\nOut of these, Level provides the greatest boon. In case of healing itself the main factor is how many points caster has in &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Hydrosophist\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; ability, however this also affects how much physical damage this skill deals to the Undead. Note that, since the skill causes physical damage to the Undead it is also affected by &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Warfare\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; ability whose bonus stacks with that of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Hydrosophist\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt;.\n properties can be affected by talents, consumable items (some of which may be affected by &lt;a href=\"Five-Star%20Diner%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Five-Star Diner&lt;/a&gt; talent) and other skills. \nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell hydrosophist spellbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in. Note that some of these may have other spell/skillbooks and goods to sell. &lt;a href=\"Almira\"&gt;Almira&lt;/a&gt; may follow the Godwoken on &lt;a href=\"The%20Lady%20Vengeance\"&gt;Lady Vengeance&lt;/a&gt; if her demands are met. Also note that &lt;a href=\"Lizard%20Dreamer\"&gt;Lizard Dreamer&lt;/a&gt; requires a persuasion check to be passed in order to speak with him, otherwise he (and the whole encampment) will turn hostile. "}
