ref=\"Books%20and%20notes%20%28Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%29\"&gt;book&lt;/a&gt;, \"&lt;a href=\"Heleon%27s%20Log\"&gt;Heleon's Log&lt;/a&gt;\".\nYou now have three (mutually exclusive) choices:"}
