{"id": "20221", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20221", "title": "Holy Fire (Status)", "text": "Holy Fire is a &lt;a href=\"Status%20Effects%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;status effect&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nHoly Fire is a positive environmental status effect which restores Vitality of the living and deals Physical damage to &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt;. Holy fire protects afflicted character from Fire damage and increases Fire Resistance by 20 %. Furthermore it grants Immunity to: \nCause.\nThere is only one viable way to create Holy Fire which is by casting &lt;a href=\"Bless%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Bless&lt;/a&gt; spell upon any \"fire surface\" which will transform it into Holy Fire for two turns. There are no spells or items that create Holy Fire directly with the only partial exception being &lt;a href=\"Summon%20Dragonling%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Summon Dragonling&lt;/a&gt; since summoned Dragonchild will bleed Holy Fire.\nStatus negation.\nThe only way to cancel out Holy fire is by casting &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; upon the afflicted character or surface which will transform it into regular fire. Any spell that causes &lt;a href=\"Necrofire%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Necrofire&lt;/a&gt; will cancel out Holy Fire. "}
{"id": "17030", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17030", "title": "Holy Hand Grenade", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Munitions%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"\"\nCharacteristics.\n is a throwable grenade that deals no damage on its own but heals afflicted living characters. However it will deal Physical Damage to all &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; characters.\nAll characters can throw this grenade. The healing output of this grenade may be increased through &lt;a href=\"Huntsman\"&gt;Huntsman&lt;/a&gt; ability by increasing bonus provided by height difference. \nSince is a grenade it is affected by &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Ambidextrous&lt;/a&gt; talent which decreases the cost of using grenades and scrolls by 1 AP when the secondary hand is free. is also affected by &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Slingshot&lt;/a&gt; which increases its range by 5 meters and by &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Far Out Man&lt;/a&gt; talent which increases range by 2 meters."}
