{"id": "4512", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4512", "title": "Hunter Necklace", "text": "The Hunter Necklace is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Accessories%23Necklaces\"&gt;special necklace&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nHunter Necklace is a special necklace that is part of the &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Set\"&gt;Hunter Set&lt;/a&gt;. The set is constituted of &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Gauntlets\"&gt;gauntlets&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Belt\"&gt;belt&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Necklace\"&gt;necklace&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Earrings\"&gt;earrings&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Ring\"&gt;ring&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Bracelets\"&gt;bracelet&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Bow\"&gt;bow&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 27 in order to be worn. When worn the necklace will boost Magic Damage by 7 points and &lt;a href=\"Firewall\"&gt;Firewall&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; by 1 point. The necklace has 1 enchantment slot. The default enchantment is Damage Aura.\nHow to Obtain.\nFound on the body of &lt;a href=\"Geshniz\"&gt;Geshniz&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Geshniz%27s%20Headquarters\"&gt;Geshniz's Headquarters&lt;/a&gt;.\nSet Properties.\nHunter Necklace is a part of the set Hunter Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Hunter Necklace primary increased attribute is Indomitable Will, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
{"id": "4515", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4515", "title": "Hunter Ring", "text": "The Hunter Ring are a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Accessories%23Rings\"&gt;special ring&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nHunter Ring is a special ring that is part of the &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Set\"&gt;Hunter Set&lt;/a&gt;. The set is constituted of &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Gauntlets\"&gt;gauntlets&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Belt\"&gt;belt&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Necklace\"&gt;necklace&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Earrings\"&gt;earrings&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Ring\"&gt;ring&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Bracelets\"&gt;bracelet&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Bow\"&gt;bow&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 28 in order to be worn. When worn the ring will boost Mana by 47 points and Critical Chance by 7 points. The ring has 1 enchantment slot. The default enchantment is Poison Aura.\nHow to Obtain.\nFound in a chest within &lt;a href=\"Raze%27s%20Flying%20Fortress\"&gt;Raze's Flying Fortress&lt;/a&gt;.\nSet Properties.\nHunter Ring is a part of the set Hunter Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Hunter Rings primary increased attribute is Critical Chance, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
{"id": "4000", "revid": "37013771", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4000", "title": "Hunter Set", "text": " is an &lt;a href=\"Armor%20Sets%20%28Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%29\"&gt;armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nThe hunter armour set is comprised of 10 armour pieces and single weapon: a bow. As a whole the set focuses on ranged attack and defence, but gives little in the way of protection if &lt;a href=\"The%20Dragon%20Knight\"&gt;The Dragon Knight&lt;/a&gt; falls into close combat. The set also gives a boost to &lt;a href=\"Indomitable%20Will\"&gt;Indomitable Will&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Conditioned%20Body\"&gt;Conditioned Body&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Critical%20Chance\"&gt;Critical Chance&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Heightened%20Reflexes\"&gt;Heightened Reflexes&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Vitality\"&gt;Vitality&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dexterity\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Mana\"&gt;Mana&lt;/a&gt;. In order to be able to wear the set fully, one must be at least level 29.\nLocations.\nEgo Draconis.\nThe entire set can be found in &lt;a href=\"Raze%27s%20Flying%20Fortress\"&gt;Raze's Flying Fortress&lt;/a&gt;."}
