{"id": "17099", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17099", "title": "Icy Nailbomb", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Munitions%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ammunition&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a throwable grenade that deals physical damage and inflicts &lt;a href=\"Bleeding%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Bleeding Status&lt;/a&gt; (3 turns) in 4 meter radius, if the Physical Armour of affected characters reaches 0. Unlike simple &lt;a href=\"Nailbomb%20Grenade\"&gt;Nailbomb grenade&lt;/a&gt; the also creates a ice surface at an area of impact in 2 meter radius.\nAll characters can throw this grenade. The damage of the grenade depends on &lt;a href=\"Warfare%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; ability and can be further increased by &lt;a href=\"Huntsman\"&gt;Huntsman&lt;/a&gt; which boosts the damage bonus provided by height difference.\nSince is a grenade it is affected by &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Ambidextrous&lt;/a&gt; talent which decreases the cost of using grenades and scrolls by 1 AP when the secondary hand is free. is also affected by &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Slingshot&lt;/a&gt; which increases its range by 5 meters and by &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Far Out Man&lt;/a&gt; talent which increases range by 2 meters."}
{"id": "12394", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12394", "title": "Icy Skin", "text": "Icy Skin is a &lt;a href=\"Polymorph%20%28Skill%20Class%29\"&gt;Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; source skill in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\n is a supportive mixed source skill that allows caster to enchant their very skin with ice for 2 turns, thus granting them immunity to &lt;a href=\"Chilled%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Chilled&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Frozen%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Frozen&lt;/a&gt; status effects alongside increased Water Resistance by 100 %. However this skill will also decrease Fire Resistance by 30 %. When caster is directly damaged they will bleed ice (note that this excludes bleeding caused by &lt;a href=\"Flesh%20Sacrifice\"&gt;Flesh Sacrifice&lt;/a&gt;). \nSince this skill applies positive status effect it will always bypass armour.\nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophy\"&gt;Hydrosophy&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Metamorphosis\"&gt;Metamorphosis&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 2 points into both &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Polymorph\"&gt;Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;abilities&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 2 free memory slots. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 500 gold. A skillbook can be crafted by combining any &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Polymorph\"&gt;Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; skillbooks out of which atleast one must be a source skillbook. Since is a mixed source skill, traders do not have the skillbook for sale.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nSkill Modifiers.\n is a supportive skill that provides clear set bonuses. As such these bonuses by themselves cannot be increased, however they can stack with other items, skills or talents that provide them.\nSince the AP cost to cast this skill is always 1 AP it cannot be lowered by any means.\nThe only way to improve this skill is to increase its range through skills or talents.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nThis skill cannot be bought or stolen from NPCs in the game."}
