{"id": "11395", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11395", "title": "Infect (Original Sin 2)", "text": "Infect is a &lt;a href=\"Necromancer%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;novice Necromancer&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\n is a offensive necromancer skill that allows caster to deal physical damage by cursing their enemy (13 meter range) with infectious disease for 2 turns. Characters without Physical Armour are afflicted with &lt;a href=\"Infected%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Infected&lt;/a&gt; status effect that lowers &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt; by 1 point (lowers maximum Vitality by 7 %) and damage attribute by 35 %. \nBecause causes infectious disease it will spread to all characters in 5 meter radius from the afflicted character and inflict them with &lt;a href=\"Infected%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Infected&lt;/a&gt; status effect which can be further passed to another character in 5 meter radius from them. Character that was originally afflicted with &lt;a href=\"Infected%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Infected&lt;/a&gt; status effect will in turn be afflicted with &lt;a href=\"Diseased%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Diseased&lt;/a&gt; status effect for 2 turns which does not spread further and cannot be further afflicted with &lt;a href=\"Infected%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Infected&lt;/a&gt; status effect. \nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Necromancy\"&gt;Necromancy&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if character is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects. skill damage is not reflected back when the target is under &lt;a href=\"Deflective%20Barrier\"&gt;Deflective Barrier&lt;/a&gt; skill (Definitive Edition only).\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 2 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Necromancer\"&gt;Necromancer&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 190 gold. A skillbook can be crafted if a scroll is combined with a &lt;a href=\"Blank%20Necromancy%20Skillbook\"&gt;Blank Necromancy Skillbook&lt;/a&gt;. Since is a novice Necromancer skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; reach level 4.\n scroll is a magical item that allows any character to cast skill, regardless of skill prerequisites, but only once. The only limiting element in casting this way is the amount of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Action%20Points\"&gt;Action Points (AP)&lt;/a&gt; character has at their disposal in current turn. The scroll is craftable, weights 0.02 and has base value of 100 gold.\nThe cost of Action Points between scroll and skill themselves remains the same. Both the scroll and the skill itself are affected by other skills and talents that may provide additional bonuses.\nSkill Modifiers.\nDamage of this skill is calculated with the following formula: (Base Damage) x (1 + Elemental Bonus%) x (1 + Attribute Bonus% + Weapon Skill Bonus %) x (1 + High Ground Bonus% + Crit Bonus%) x ( 1 + Misc Bonus %)\nThe damage of this skill is affected by the following attributes of the caster:\nOut of these the most effect on the damage have Level and then Warfare ability as the latter increases damage by 5 % per point. Level provides greatest boost to the damage done. Intelligence provides the lowest bonus out of the three (3 points in Intelligence are equal to 1 point of Warfare).\nWhen it comes to enemies they may resist water damage if they have: Physical Immunity Status. There are no actual resistances that may lower physical damage done.\nSince is a skill requiring Necromancer ability to cast on its own, it will cause caster to heal from damage done directly to the Vitality of target enemy. The health received is affected by damage done to the Vitality and by points invested in Necromancer ability itself.\n properties can be affected by talents, consumable items (some of which may be affected by &lt;a href=\"Five-Star%20Diner%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Five-Star Diner&lt;/a&gt; talent) and other skills.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell necromancer spellbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in. Note that some of these may have other spell/skillbooks and goods to sell. Out of these only \"&lt;a href=\"Tarquin\"&gt;Tarquin&lt;/a&gt;\" is guaranteed to follow the &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; as they travel with &lt;a href=\"The%20Lady%20Vengeance\"&gt;Lady Vengeance&lt;/a&gt;. \"&lt;a href=\"Jahan\"&gt;Jahan&lt;/a&gt;\" may join the Godwoken on the ship as well if his demands are met. "}
{"id": "6036", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=6036", "title": "Infectious Flame", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Pyrokinetic%20%28Original%20Sin%29\"&gt;Pyrokinetic spell&lt;/a&gt; in ' and '.\nOriginal Sin.\nDescription.\nCast a magical flame that forks on impact and does X-Y fire damage to each target. \nForks up to 5 times looking for next target in a 7 meters radius. \n70% base chance to set \nCan target terrain to create fire surface, burn ooze, evaporate water, or melt ice.\nEnhanced Edition.\nDescription.\nCast a magical flame that forks on impact and does X-Y fire damage to each target.\n100% chance to set Burning status for 2 turns.\nForks up to 5 times looking for next target in a 7.0m radius. \nBurning does fire damage over time. \nCan target terrain to create fire surface, burn ooze, evaporate water, or melt ice."}
