{"id": "14978", "revid": "53418829", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14978", "title": "Investigate the Dark Cave", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20quests\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLook for the missing boy, and kill the Vampire.\nWalkthrough.\nUpon travelling to &lt;a href=\"Verdistis\"&gt;Verdistis&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt; may encounter &lt;a href=\"Sir%20Markham\"&gt;Sir Markham&lt;/a&gt; fighting trolls. After dispatching them, he asks Lucian to investigate a cave nearby, which he believes holds an evil presence.\nTrue enough, inside the cave is a vampire who is about to feed on a little boy, Marty. \nLucian now has two options;\nIf Lucian is investigating &lt;a href=\"George%20Murdered%21\"&gt;George's murder&lt;/a&gt;, he can ask the vampire about . But this vampire has never been in &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt;, nor does he know any &lt;a href=\"George\"&gt;George&lt;/a&gt;.\nThis quest also involves the same boy &lt;a href=\"Caroline%20%28Divine%20Divinity%29\"&gt;Caroline&lt;/a&gt; is looking for, and so, the decision will affect the outcome of both quests.\nFor saving Marty, Caroline rewards 11k xp. She can be found at the southern entrance of &lt;a href=\"Rivertown%20market\"&gt;Rivertown market&lt;/a&gt;\nNo matter the decision made, this quest opens up the Kill the vampire quest, since there is a vampire on the loose.\nKill the Vampire.\nThe Vampire is a threat to the surrounding areas, so it must be killed. The door leading to it is locked. To open the door, either use &lt;a href=\"Telekinesis%20%28Divine%20Divinity%29\"&gt;Telekinesis&lt;/a&gt; on the nearby lever, OR lockpick the door (&lt;a href=\"Lockpick%20%28Divine%20Divinity%29\"&gt;Lockpick&lt;/a&gt; rank 2 required). The vampire attacks when his coffin is opened. Killing it rewards experience and +3 reputation."}
