{"id": "20289", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20289", "title": "Conditioned Body", "text": "Conditioned Body is a game mechanic in \"\". \nDescription.\nConditioned Body a mechanic that serves as an additional protection from spells that could harm the Slayer. When slayer is struck by &lt;a href=\"Firewall\"&gt;Firewall&lt;/a&gt; its flames will inflict \"Burning\" upon them which will last a certain ammount of time. Conditioned Body shortens the time this effect lasts until it is cancelled. It does not protect directly from the harmful effects but it shortens their influence. \nAcquisition.\nConditioned Body is a mechanic that derives its value from &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; attribute and bonuses from equipment. Increasing Strength will boost the value of Conditioned Body. "}
