{"id": "12401", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12401", "title": "Corpse Explosion", "text": "Corpse Explosion is a &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Pyrokinetic\"&gt;Pyrokinetic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Necromancer\"&gt;Necromancer&lt;/a&gt; skill in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nExplode target corpse, dealing physical damage in the area.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 1 point into both &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Pyrokinetic\"&gt;Pyrokinetic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Necromancer\"&gt;Necromancer&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;abilities&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 190 gold. A skillbook can be crafted if a any non-source &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Pyrokinetic\"&gt;Pyrokinetic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Necromancer\"&gt;Necromancer&lt;/a&gt; skillbooks are combined. Since is a mixed skill, traders do not have the skillbook for sale.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nThis skill cannot be bought or stolen from NPCs in the game."}
