{"id": "12364", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12364", "title": "Cryogenic Stasis", "text": "Cryogenic Stasis is a &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophist%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;adept Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\n is a supportive hydrosophist skill that allows caster to set &lt;a href=\"Permafrost%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Permafrost&lt;/a&gt; status effect on their ally. This status drastically increases all resistances (as well as granting resistances to Physical and Piercing damage) alongside providing immunity to large variety of negative status effects (listed below). While target character will be incapacitated for 1 turn they will be healed after the effect ends. Note that this applies also to &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt;, rendering this skill the only Hydrosophist skill that heals Undead.\nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Hydrosophy\"&gt;Hydrosophy&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects. \nResistances granted:\nStatus effect immunities granted:\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 3 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Hydrosophist\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 500 gold. Since is an adept Hydrosophist skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; reach level 9.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nSkill Modifiers.\n is a supportive skill whose effects depend on the following characteristics of the caster:\nOutside of the Level of the caster only their &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Hydrosophist\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; ability can influence the amount of healing gained by . \n properties can be affected by talents and other skills only. \nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell hydrosophist spellbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in. Note that some of these may have other spell/skillbooks and goods to sell. &lt;a href=\"Almira\"&gt;Almira&lt;/a&gt; may follow the Godwoken on &lt;a href=\"The%20Lady%20Vengeance\"&gt;Lady Vengeance&lt;/a&gt; if her demands are met. Also note that &lt;a href=\"Lizard%20Dreamer\"&gt;Lizard Dreamer&lt;/a&gt; requires a persuasion check to be passed in order to speak with him, otherwise he (and the whole encampment) will turn hostile. "}
