{"id": "20103", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20103", "title": "Cursed Oil Infusion", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Geomancer%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Geomancer&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Summoning\"&gt;Summoning source skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nCursed Oil Infusion is a spell that changes &lt;a href=\"Conjure%20Incarnate\"&gt;Incarnate&lt;/a&gt;'s element to earth, unlocking &lt;a href=\"Fossil%20Strike\"&gt;Fossil Strike&lt;/a&gt; spell. In addition to this it will unlock a Source spell &lt;a href=\"Dust%20Blast\"&gt;Dust Blast&lt;/a&gt;. \nThe spell has been added to the game as part of Pet Power gift bag and as such it can only be crafted and used when the gift bag has been activated.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nThis source skill cannot be bought or stolen from any NPCs in the game.\nGift Bag: Pet Power.\nGift Bag: Pet Power allows this skill to be used on any summoned creature. This gift bag also shortens the cooldown of this skill from 3 turns to 1 turn. Following table shows what skills will specific summoned entity gain from . Note that there are no changes to the skill and bonuses granted by the skill to the &lt;a href=\"Conjure%20Incarnate\"&gt;Incarnate&lt;/a&gt;, likewise all summoned entities gain source skill &lt;a href=\"Dust%20Blast\"&gt;Dust Blast&lt;/a&gt; and + 2 Source points."}
