{"id": "12418", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12418", "title": "Daggers Drawn (Original Sin 2)", "text": "Daggers drawn is an &lt;a href=\"Scoundrel%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;expert Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Sourcery%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;source&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nWhirl into a barrage of 5 stabs, each dealing physical damage.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 3 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Scoundrel\"&gt;Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 2 free memory slots. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 750 gold. Since is a expert Scoundrel skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once player character or their &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Companions\"&gt;companions&lt;/a&gt; reach level 13.\nSince is a weapon based skill and as such it does not have a scroll. It is also not possible to craft a skillbook.\nSkill Modifiers.\nScales off basic attacks and gets a bonus from Finesse.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell scoundrel skillbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in. Note that some of these may have other spell/skillbooks and goods to sell."}
