{"id": "12409", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12409", "title": "Deploy Mass Traps", "text": "Deploy Mass Traps is a &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Pyrokinetic\"&gt;Pyrokinetic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Huntsman\"&gt;Huntsman&lt;/a&gt; source skill in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nThrow 4 explosive traps at target locations. Each trap takes a turn to activate. When active, trap will explode when a character approaches it.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 2 points into both &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Pyrokinetic\"&gt;Pyrokinetic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Huntsman\"&gt;Huntsman&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;abilities&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 2 free memory slots. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 500 gold. A skillbook can be crafted by combining any &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Pyrokinetic\"&gt;Pyrokinetic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Huntsman\"&gt;Huntsman&lt;/a&gt; skillbooks out of which atleast one must be a source skillbook. Since is a mixed source skill, traders do not have the skillbook for sale.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll."}
