{"id": "14920", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14920", "title": "Dwarven Bread Inn", "text": " is an inn in &lt;a href=\"Rivellon\"&gt;Rivellon&lt;/a&gt;.\nBackground.\n&lt;a href=\"Sean%20%28Divine%20Divinity%29\"&gt;Sean&lt;/a&gt; has been running the inn for four years, since his father's death.\nLayout.\nMain floor.\nThe Entrance leads straight into the saloon. Behind the counter in the saloon are four wine barrels and one bigger beer barrel. To the right of the saloon are a kitchen, a small storage, and after that quarters for the staff. A locked (lvl 1 &lt;a href=\"Lockpick%20%28Divine%20Divinity%29\"&gt;lockpick&lt;/a&gt;) wooden cupboard is in the kitchen. Next to eastern exit is also a cask of beer.\nGuest rooms are to the left of the saloon, consisting of four rooms.\n&lt;a href=\"Krasnegar\"&gt;Krasnegar&lt;/a&gt; stays at the room behind the Inn, and after he is gone to travel, a dog named &lt;a href=\"Dog%23Lar\"&gt;Lar&lt;/a&gt; is in the room instead. In this room there is also a unique crossbow. Next to the crossbow sits a locked (lvl 3) chest.\nAnother locked chest (lvl 3) is found in the eastern guest room. The bronze key for this chest is lying on the table in the same room.\nThe southwestern guest room has another locked (lvl 3) chest.\nBehind the building is a small area for chickens. There is also an &lt;a href=\"Augmentor\"&gt;Augmentor&lt;/a&gt; just north of the building.\nThe Dwarven Bread Inn teleporter is also just northwest of the Inn.\nA ladder next to the kitchen leads down to the basement.\nBasement.\nThe basement acts both as a storage and boxing area. The boxing arena is in the western room, which includes, along with boxing crowd, a locked chest which can be opened with bronze key lying on the table next to the boxing ring. Next to the chest on table &lt;a href=\"Magical%20Tragedies%20Part%20VII\"&gt;Magical Tragedies Part VII&lt;/a&gt; can be found. \nThe eastern room is a small food storage with two big casks of beer.\nThe southern room is locked."}
