{"id": "10939", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=10939", "title": "Earth Resistance Potion (Original Sin 2)", "text": "The is a &lt;a href=\"Consumables%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;consumable item&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nEarth resistance potion is a consumable potion that grants + 15 % Earth resistance for 3 turns. If character has \"&lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt;\", the potion will grant + 30 % Earth resistance instead of + 15 %. The potions weight is 0.25 and its value is 30 gold.\nMedium earth resistance potion is a consumable potion that grants + 50 % Earth resistance for 3 turns. If character has \"Five-Star Diner talent\", the potion will grant + 100 % Earth resistance instead of + 50 %. The potions weight is 0.25 and its value is 45 gold.\nLarge earth resistance potion is a consumable potion that grants 75 % Earth resistance for 2 turns. If character has \"Five-Star Diner talent\", the potion will grant + 150 % Earth resistance instead of + 75 %. The potions weight is 0.25 and its value is 150 gold.\nHuge earth resistance potion is a consumable potion that grants 90 % Earth resistance for 2 turns. If character has \"Five-Star Diner talent\", the potion will grant + 180 % Earth resistance instead of + 90 %. The potions weight is 0.25 and its value is 450 gold.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing NPCs sell a large variety of potions and thus have a solid chance (not guaranteed) of having in their stock. Note that as a consumable item may be very randomly sold by other NPCs."}
