{"id": "14832", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14832", "title": "Energy Cage", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20skills%23Way%20of%20the%20mage\"&gt;Mage skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\nIf succesful, the spell ensnares an enemy inside a cage, stopping its movement and making it unable to attack. &lt;a href=\"Limbs%20of%20Lead\"&gt;Limbs of Lead&lt;/a&gt; is a similar skill, but it only slows an enemy.\nLocation.\nSkillbook can be found on bookshelves and bought from NPC's."}
