{"id": "22547", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=22547", "title": "Escaping Stormfist Castle", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20quests\"&gt;main quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDetailed Walkthrough.\nEscaping Stormfist Castle is a main quest that is automatically accepted as part of the main quest &lt;a href=\"An%20Appointment%20With%20the%20New%20Ruler%20of%20Ferol\"&gt;An Appointment With the New Ruler of Ferol&lt;/a&gt; where duke &lt;a href=\"Janus%20Ferol\"&gt;Janus Ferol&lt;/a&gt; appoints you as his Lord Protector till you die or 40 years pass. \nThis quest can be only completed by completing all 6 sub-quests of the main quest An Appointment With the New Ruler of Ferol where you will do some menial tasks for Janus. At the final sub-quest The Merchant's meeting you will be scolded for failing to kill the attacking &lt;a href=\"orcs\"&gt;orcs&lt;/a&gt; fast enough and Janus will have you thrown out of the castle. After you are led out of the castle by the guards, you will be approached by Elona who will reveal to be a &lt;a href=\"Iona\"&gt;Iona&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;a href=\"Black%20Ring\"&gt;Black Ring&lt;/a&gt; cultist and superior of doctor &lt;a href=\"Elrath\"&gt;Elrath&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe quest is automatically completed once you are led out of the castle. Note that you will not be allowed to enter it again through the main gate."}
