{"id": "3984", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3984", "title": "Eternal Commitment", "text": "Eternal Commitment is a &lt;a href=\"Flames%20of%20Vengeance%20quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; received from the dying &lt;a href=\"Champions%20of%20Aleroth\"&gt;Champion&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Decimus\"&gt;Decimus&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;a href=\"Healers%27%20House\"&gt;Healers' House&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Great%20Market\"&gt;Great Market&lt;/a&gt; district of &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt; during the events of \"\". \nDetailed Walkthrough.\nDecimus is seeking some peace of mind in his final hours. His wife has passed away during the siege and he'd like you to retrieve her favorite ring.\nYou'll need to gain access to &lt;a href=\"Crow%27s%20Nest\"&gt;Crow's Nest&lt;/a&gt; by completing the quest &lt;a href=\"Bark%20up%20the%20Right%20Tree\"&gt;Bark up the Right Tree&lt;/a&gt; first. You'll find &lt;a href=\"Decimus%27%20House\"&gt;Decimus' House&lt;/a&gt; east of &lt;a href=\"Henry%20and%20Eleanor%27s%20House\"&gt;Henry and Eleanor's House&lt;/a&gt; and southeast of &lt;a href=\"Crowell%27s%20House\"&gt;Crowell's House&lt;/a&gt;. Inside you'll encounter the bandit &lt;a href=\"Carmina\"&gt;Carmina&lt;/a&gt; who is a target of the quest &lt;a href=\"A%20Hunting%20We%20Shall%20Go%20Once%20More\"&gt;A Hunting We Shall Go Once More&lt;/a&gt;. After defeating Carmina and her thugs, take &lt;a href=\"Livia%27s%20Ring\"&gt;Livia's Ring&lt;/a&gt; from one of the small lockboxes.\nYou can either give the ring to Decimus to complete this quest, or give it to &lt;a href=\"Astridax\"&gt;Astridax&lt;/a&gt; for the quest &lt;a href=\"Sinister%20Motives\"&gt;Sinister Motives&lt;/a&gt; instead."}
