{"id": "13096", "revid": "31775388", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=13096", "title": "Evelyn", "text": " is a female &lt;a href=\"human\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt; sourcerer who came to &lt;a href=\"Cyseal\"&gt;Cyseal&lt;/a&gt; in 4 AR.\nBackground.\nEvelyn is first introduced as a healer apprenticed to &lt;a href=\"Thelyron%20Hashnitor\"&gt;Thelyron&lt;/a&gt;. She had discovered healing items known as blood stones which could cure advanced injuries, and was deciding which of two patients she should use her last blood stone on. The Source Hunters can make the decision for her. Much to Thelyron's annoyance, she keeps the source of the blood stones a secret.\nShe is first named as a suspect in &lt;a href=\"Zombie%20Jake\"&gt;Councillor Jake&lt;/a&gt;'s murder when &lt;a href=\"Robin\"&gt;Robin&lt;/a&gt;, the undertaker, mentions she had opportunity to steal his body. Esmeralda also suspects her of something, saying she saw evil in Evelyn's eyes, after which Evelyn abruptly leaves Cyseal. Thelyron allows the Source Hunters to investigate her house, where they find a letter directing them to a hideout near a secluded beach. The letter also indicates her involvement in &lt;a href=\"Cecil%27s%20Mighty%20Staff\"&gt;Dietmar's theft of the Staff of Pergamon&lt;/a&gt;.\nAfter the Source Hunters reveal Evelyn's lair with the use of a spell, they meet several Immaculate cultists (including a few &lt;a href=\"Orc\"&gt;Orc&lt;/a&gt;s). The humans must be fought, but the Orcs can be persuaded to leave. Evelyn is downstairs, next to Jake's undead body; &lt;a href=\"Leandra\"&gt;Leandra&lt;/a&gt; chastises her for her recklessness, and disappears after spotting the Source Hunters. Evelyn then attacks the Source Hunters after a brief conversation. When fought, Evelyn summons several creatures to aid her, as well as casting elemental spells.\nAfter her death, Jake tells the Source Hunters that he was actually killed by Leandra's sister, &lt;a href=\"Icara\"&gt;Icara&lt;/a&gt;, and Evelyn had only stolen his body so she could try to learn his secrets."}
