{"id": "11558", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11558", "title": "Farsight Infusion", "text": "Farsight Infusion is a &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Summoning\"&gt;starter Summoning&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\n is a supportive summoning skill that allows caster to imbue their summoned Incarnate for 3 turns or until the Incarnate expires. The skill will allow the Incarnate to cast &lt;a href=\"Ranged%20Attack%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Ranged Attack&lt;/a&gt; skill whilst increasing their Damage by 25 % and granting Magic Armour. \nUnlike elemental infusion skills, this infusion skill can be combined with other infusion skills such as &lt;a href=\"Power%20Infusion\"&gt;Power Infusion&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Infusion\"&gt;Fire Infusion&lt;/a&gt; without it being cancelled. This skill however can be used only on the Incarnate and cannot be used on other summoned creatures and totems.\nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Summoning\"&gt;Summoning&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 1 point into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Summoning\"&gt;Summoning&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 120 gold. Since is a starter Summoning skill, it is available right from the start of the game. Traders selling Summoning skillbooks will have this book for sale since the start of the game as well. \n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nSkill Modifiers.\n is a supportive skill whose effects depend on the following characteristics of the caster:\nOutside of the Level of the caster only their &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Hydrosophist\"&gt;Hydrosophist&lt;/a&gt; ability can influence the amount of Magic Armour gained by . Damage bonus and skill granted through skill cannot be influenced.\n skill properties can be affected by talents and other skills only.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell summoning spellbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in.\nGift Bag: Pet Power.\nGift Bag: Pet Power allows this skill to be used on any summoned creature (except Totems). This gift bag also shortens the cooldown of this skill from 3 turns to 1 turn. Unlike other Infusion skills, the Farsight infusion will always grant summoned creature only the &lt;a href=\"Ranged%20Attack%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Ranged Attack&lt;/a&gt; skill as well as provide increased damage and Magic Armour."}
