{"id": "17870", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17870", "title": "Find Clues About Wares", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDetails Walkthrough.\nSomething is off with the cart attack. It looks like an orc attack (there are orcs in nearby areas), but there are doubts.\nHead back to cart, and follow the blood trail, east from &lt;a href=\"Dwarven%20Bread%20Inn\"&gt;Dwarven Bread Inn&lt;/a&gt;. First you'll find the dead bodies of the cart drivers, and further to the east the trail leads to a cave.\nIn the back of the cave, you'll find the &lt;a href=\"Letter%20from%20Pedro%20to%20Victorio\"&gt;Letter from Pedro to Victorio&lt;/a&gt;. Take this letter to &lt;a href=\"Marcus\"&gt;Marcus&lt;/a&gt;, but you'll need to deal with &lt;a href=\"Victorio\"&gt;Victorio&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Melora\"&gt;Melora&lt;/a&gt; first. Of these Victorio is the bigger threat, being a melee fighter, whereas Melora tends to stay out of melee range.\nYou could also escape the battle by using a &lt;a href=\"Teleporter%20pyramid\"&gt;Teleporter pyramid&lt;/a&gt;, Victorio and Melora will still be in the cave, even after the black market mystery is solved.\nShowing the letter to Marcus ends this quest, rewarding a 10 disposition increase with Marcus, along with some experience."}
