{"id": "2806", "revid": "47788234", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2806", "title": "Kali's Flying Fortress", "text": "Kali's Flying Fortress is located in Rivertown Gorge, just south of the &lt;a href=\"Orobas%20Fjords\"&gt;Orobas Fjords&lt;/a&gt;.\nBackground.\nRivertown Gorge was essentially destroyed by &lt;a href=\"Damian\"&gt;Damian&lt;/a&gt;'s forces, so her fortress is all there is.\nLayout.\nThe enemies faced here are mostly level 29 with &lt;a href=\"Kali\"&gt;Kali&lt;/a&gt;, the leader, being level 30. The airborne enemies (Gas Floaters and Damian Dragons) range from level 26-28. There are some &lt;a href=\"herbs\"&gt;herbs&lt;/a&gt; scattered throughout the fortress (including &lt;a href=\"Farhangite\"&gt;Farhangite&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Whisperwood\"&gt;Whisperwood&lt;/a&gt;), as well as a handful of chests.\nOn the large northern platform, not far from the entrance, there is a teleporter to the fortress' small storage area. There are only a few enemies inside, and a chest containing both &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20Earrings\"&gt;Hunter Earrings&lt;/a&gt; from the &lt;a href=\"Hunter%20armour%20set\"&gt;Hunter armour set&lt;/a&gt; and a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Armor\"&gt;Plate Dragon Helmet&lt;/a&gt;. Outside the storage area, on a lower level of the same platform, a chest contains the &lt;a href=\"Scorpion%20Ring\"&gt;Scorpion Ring&lt;/a&gt;, part of the &lt;a href=\"Scorpion\"&gt;Scorpion&lt;/a&gt; armour set.\nOn the southern large platform the teleporter to the fortress' headquarters is found. Once inside continue through, pulling the levers at the end of the hallways to the east and west to open doors further along. Proceed to the southeast corner to obtain a key needed to open the door to Kali's chamber (the chest here contains random loot as well as the key).\nInside her chamber, a conversation with Kali automatically begins. Be sure to &lt;a href=\"mindread\"&gt;mindread&lt;/a&gt; her to obtain &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s%20Helmet\"&gt;Ulthring's Helmet&lt;/a&gt; of the &lt;a href=\"Ulthring%27s\"&gt;Ulthring&lt;/a&gt; armour set following her death. When killed, she drops &lt;a href=\"The%20Demon%20Wars\"&gt;The Demon Wars&lt;/a&gt; (a special &lt;a href=\"Skill%20Book\"&gt;skill book&lt;/a&gt; and quest item for &lt;a href=\"By%20the%20Book\"&gt;By the Book&lt;/a&gt; that rewards 3 &lt;a href=\"Skills%20%28Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%29\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; points). She also drops a &lt;a href=\"Folded%20Letter\"&gt;Folded Letter&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=\"Damian\"&gt;Damian&lt;/a&gt; and a powerful sword called &lt;a href=\"Myrthos\"&gt;Myrthos&lt;/a&gt; (quest item for &lt;a href=\"Murder%20for%20Myrthos\"&gt;Murder for Myrthos&lt;/a&gt;), along with random loot. You can also pick up a copy of &lt;a href=\"History%20of%20the%20Damned%20One%2C%20Part%20VI\"&gt;History of the Damned One, Part VI&lt;/a&gt; in her chamber."}
