oms coming off it. The first room on the south west wall is locked and requires a skilled locksmith to pick the lock. Within it is an unlocked chest. In the next room (south east corner) the merchant &lt;a href=\"Sereth\"&gt;Sereth&lt;/a&gt; who specialises in &lt;a href=\"Scoundrel\"&gt;Scoundrel&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Witchcraft\"&gt;Witchcraft&lt;/a&gt; skillbooks and her bodyguard can be found. The next room is rented by the &lt;a href=\"elf\"&gt;elf&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Eglandaer\"&gt;Eglandaer&lt;/a&gt;. The final room appears to be a shared bathroom with several wash tubs and folded clothes. On the wall opposite is another room with an array of beds and mattresses along with five chests."}
