{"id": "11636", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11636", "title": "Kniles", "text": "Kniles is a magister located in\u00a0&lt;a href=\"The%20Flenser%27s%20Playground\"&gt;The Flenser's Playground&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0inside Fort Joy in 1242 AD.\nBackground.\nKniles the Flenser is a sadistic &lt;a href=\"The%20Magisters\"&gt;Magister&lt;/a&gt; who resides within his section of &lt;a href=\"Fort%20Joy%20Prison\"&gt;Fort Joy Prison&lt;/a&gt; known as &lt;a href=\"The%20Flenser%27s%20Playground\"&gt;The Flenser's Playground&lt;/a&gt;. He is the son of the inkeeper &lt;a href=\"Prudence\"&gt;Prudence&lt;/a&gt; who works at &lt;a href=\"The%20Black%20Bull\"&gt;Black Bull&lt;/a&gt; inn in &lt;a href=\"Driftwood\"&gt;Driftwood&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=\"Reaper%27s%20Coast\"&gt;Reaper's Coast&lt;/a&gt;. \nHe has an uncontrollable obsession with blood, killing, dissecting people and other grisly acts which he had since his childhood where he experimented on his friends in secret. His terrible actions made his mother make a deal with an &lt;a href=\"Adramahlihk\"&gt;archdemon&lt;/a&gt; in order to no longer perceive him as a monster. \nLoot Table.\nFollowing table shows all possible items which can be found in the corpse of Kniles."}
