{"id": "17671", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17671", "title": "To the Hall of Echoes", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Quests%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;main quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDetailed walkthrough.\nAfter you had successfully defended Malady you will be transported into the Hall of Echoes. There a dialogue describing the place will be initiated. After the dialogue walk down the path and if your character has any mobility skill like &lt;a href=\"Spread%20Your%20Wings\"&gt;Spread Your Wings&lt;/a&gt; use it to access the cliff on the right side. There you will find &lt;a href=\"Tormented%20Soul\"&gt;High Quality Tormented Soul&lt;/a&gt; and a teleport behind it, pick up the soul and use the teleport to get back. The teleport will return you on the crossroads. There turn left and go across the chasm which will gradually materialise a bridge as you approach. \nOnce you are across the chasm you will see at the roots of a spectral tree hanged all of the &lt;a href=\"Seven%20Gods\"&gt;Seven Gods&lt;/a&gt;. In order to progress cast &lt;a href=\"Bless\"&gt;Bless&lt;/a&gt; upon the Seven God which had spoken with you in a previous vision (the one where you received the skill Bless), if you play as Lohse cast Bless upon any of the Seven Gods and second \"Lohse\" will appear and talk with you. Afterwards you will be teleported back upon the Lady Vengeance and a dialogue with your party members will be initiated. Once you are done, enter the ship and go to the Lady Vengeance lower deck, where &lt;a href=\"Alexandar\"&gt;Alexandar&lt;/a&gt; used to be imprisoned. Once you enter the Lower Deck you will meet with the spirits of the &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; you did not choose to have in your party, as well as Malady who will teleport you back to &lt;a href=\"Rivellon\"&gt;Rivellon&lt;/a&gt;."}
