{"id": "10159", "revid": "2056997", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=10159", "title": "Two-handed (DOS EE)", "text": "General.\nThe Two Handed skill increases the critical strike chance and damage multiplier of your attacks and abilities, as abilities can critically strike! This skill is one of the most value-per-point in the game, as you can potentially crit 5 or 6 enemies at once with good positioning and ability usage. It does have the drawback of being rather luck based, however."}
